Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.16,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Need to go. To the.}Đi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:29.94,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Need to go. To the. Bathroom.}Thủ dâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.80,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Can't stand her rambling.}Chẳng hiểu cô ta nói gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:38.04,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{What Ikishima-san said isn't just rambling.}Ikishima không nói sai đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.54,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Jabami Yumeko is a housepet but that's what makes her terrifying.}Jabami Yumeko là thú cưng, chính vì thế nó làm cô ta đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:47.38,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{If she uses her right to a public match against the president...}Nếu cô ta sử dụng quyền của mình để thách đấu Hội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.22,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Depending on the game...}Dựa theo luật...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.56,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{President becomes a housepet.}Hội trưởng có khả năng thành thú cưng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:56.06,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{She's no exception to that rule.}Ai thua đều như nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.08,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I won't let that happen!}Còn lâu mới xảy ra chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.40,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I'm against that as well.}Tôi cũng phản đối.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:04.94,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{But more importantly, can't we collect what she owes us to cut down on her cash?}Quan trọng hơn, sao chúng ta không ép cô ta trả nợ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:09.14,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Did you forget? The president forbade that.}Quên rồi à? Hội trưởng cấm điều đó.
