Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:14.36,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I like what I see.}Ừm. Được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.58,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Leave Yumeko-chan to me!}Để Yumeko cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:21.20,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,650,,{Episode 8: The loving girl.}Tập 8: Cô bé dễ thương
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.54,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Yumemite, you...}Yumemite, cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:20.98,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,Yumemite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.18,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I can take on Yumeko-chan by myself!}Tôi sẽ xử lý Yumeko cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:31.00,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I see... That's true, you'd certainly know how to morally destroy her.\NShould be an easy task.}Ừm...Đúng là cô có thể xử lý Yumeko bằng cách đạo\N đức nhất. Nhiệm vụ này sẽ trở nên dễ dàng hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.08,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I know, right?}Phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.06,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{It's a great opportunity, I want to make it flashy!}Hiếm lắm mới có cơ hội, tôi muốn làm nó thật hoành tráng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.90,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Manyuda-kun, I want you to help me out.}Manyuda cũng giúp nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:43.26,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Alright. I'll make sure everything goes smooth.}Được, tôi sẽ lo mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:47.28,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Please, wait! We need to wait for our president's orders!}Khoan! Chúng ta nên chờ Hội trưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.38,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{This is bad...}Tệ rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.72,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{I can't stop them.}Mình không thể cản họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:56.16,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{And what does the president intends to do, I don't evenâ€”}Ngay cả Hội trưởng đang làm gì mình cũng không biết...
