Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.24,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Why is she so cheery?}Sao cậu ta có vẻ vui thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.04,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Don't know. She's been like that since this morning.}Không biết nữa. Sáng giờ cười suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.68,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{It's probably because of that letter.}Quả nhiên là do lá thư đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.84,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Letter?}Thư?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.76,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Jabami-senpai!}Chị Jabami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.74,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{It's been a while.}Đã lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.10,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{First-year cherry blossom class. Itsuki Sumeragi!}Năm nhất lớp Anh đào, Sumeragi Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:37.46,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Tada! Japanese-style Mont-blanc cake from Seifuudou. A present!}Đây là bánh Mont blanc kiểu Nhật từ Seifuudou. Quà cho chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.14,TrebuchetMS,,0,0,0,,{Ah, that'sâ€”}A, đó là--
